  "body_text": null,
  "page": null,
  "source": "[\\set.theoretic.domain{R}]\nDefines: D is \\set\nwhen: R is \\set\nexpresses:\n. forAll: a is \\set\n  then:\n  . have: a \"in\" D\n    iff:\n    . exists: b is \\set\n      suchThat: \\set.theoretic.ordered.pair:of{a}:and{b} \"in\" R\nDocumented:\n. called: \"domain of $R?$\"\n. written: \"\\operatorname{dom}(R?)\"\n. description: \"The domain of a relation $R$, the set $\\{a \\mid \\exists b \\text{ such that } a \\mathbin{R} b\\}$ of first coordinates of the pairs in $R$.\"\nId: \"046391ea-6a1b-452e-9ef5-07319ebd5362\"",
